<p></p>
<h1 id=3D"AccountMFEHeaderAnalysis-UI-EXPAPIRequestHeaderParameters">UI-EXP=
 API Request Header Parameters</h1>
<p><a href=3D"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projects/UI-WWW/repos/ui=
-framework-npm/browse/core/api-client" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofol=
low">ApiClient</a> helper library injects the bellow header/query parameter=
s based on received request.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 51.=
5225%;">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 20.6627%;">
<col style=3D"width: 17.7447%;">
<col style=3D"width: 20.8993%;">
<col style=3D"width: 12.6185%;">
<col style=3D"width: 28.0761%;">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">EXP API Header</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Reason needed</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Expected Value</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Framework GAP</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Comment</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">x-authorization</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Authentication</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">JWT token</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">NO</span></=
p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">x-messageId</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Platform mandatory header</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">UUID v4</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">NO</span></=
p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">x-appCorrelationId</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Platform mandatory header</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">UUID v4</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">NO</span></=
p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">x-brandId</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Platform mandatory header</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>WBC</strong></p><p>if the customer br=
owses a Westpac domain</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">NO</span></=
p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>Customers: derived from URL</li>
<li>Staff: derived from token role</li>
<li>In local development: app-config</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">x-channelType</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Platform mandatory header</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Per logic</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">NO</span></=
p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">This header is deprecated and will not be used f=
or downstream calls</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">x-deviceExperience</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Platform mandatory header</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Per logic</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">NO</s=
pan></span></p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span>ApiClient helper will inject this heade=
r parameter.</span></p>Non-functional header to provide telemetry and debug=
ging aids when logged to Splunk. The proposal is to have a single string en=
coded value with the below attributes to start off with. Other attributes c=
an be added as the need arisesTYPE: app | browser, PLATFORM: ios | andriod =
| windows | linux | macos, VIEWPORT: xs | sm | md | lg, ORIENTATION: portra=
it | landscape</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">x-originatingSystemId</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Platform mandatory header</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>A014A6</strong></p><p>(CCMP's alfabet=
 id)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">NO</span></=
p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">ApiClient&nbsp;helper will inject this header pa=
rameter.<br>
 This will always correspond to the Alfabet id of the main consuming SPA al=
though various micro-frontends and widgets may have separate ownership.</td=
>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">x-originatingBSB</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">GCM API requires us to provide this as a mandato=
ry header.</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><u><em>CCMP team to decide on the value</em></u></p>
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M058573" =
href=3D"/display/~M058573" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1125291984" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Ave Cahyadi</a>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-moved">NO</span></p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Developers should follow instructions <a href=
=3D"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projects/UI-WWW/repos/ui-framework=
-npm/browse/core/api-client" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow"> here=
 </a>to user the below:</p><p>`app/delegation/originatingBSB/SET` - `app/de=
legation/originatingBSB/UNSET`</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h1 id=3D"AccountMFEHeaderAnalysis-EXPAPI-DownstreamRequestHeaderParameters=
">EXP API-Downstream Request Header Parameters</h1>
<p><a href=3D"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projects/UI-WWW/repos/no=
