<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">x-organisationId</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Platform mandatory header</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Sourced from the UI request based on x-brandI=
D.</p><p>if x-brandId =3D=3D "WBC"</p><p>x-organisationId =3D <strong>WPAC<=
/strong></p></td>
